metadata.name: from milan with love
metadata.description:
Kit from Milan visited Cologne and we shot some Ilford HP5 black-and-white films with my beloved Contax G2. This is one of the pictures taken during our shoot. It was developed and digitized by a photo lab in Germany. The scan is the basis of this photographic NFT.

-
3649 x 5444 px // 240dpi // 10mb // .jpg

Collector can claim a signed A5 physical print. 

Minted in January 2022 by @benhammer on Foundation.app as part of the "Analogue Century" Collection. 

#001
